== Remarks ==
[[SDL_QuitEvent]] is a member of the [[SDL_Event]] union and is used when an event of type SDL_QUIT is reported.  You would access it through the event's <code>quit</code> field.

Please refer to [[SDL_EventType#SDL_QUIT|the discussion of SDL_QUIT]] for more details.

